graph TB
    subgraph SDK["CodeFlare SDK (Python Client Library)"]
        direction TB

        subgraph RayModule["ray module"]
            Cluster["ray.cluster<br/>Cluster Class<br/>(lifecycle management)"]
            Config["ray.cluster.config<br/>ClusterConfiguration<br/>(dataclass)"]
            GenYAML["ray.cluster.generate_yaml<br/>YAML Generation Engine"]
            AppWrapper["ray.appwrapper<br/>AWManager"]
            RayClient["ray.client<br/>RayJobClient"]

            Config -->|configures| Cluster
            Cluster -->|calls| GenYAML
            Cluster -->|optional wrap| AppWrapper
            Cluster -->|job submission| RayClient
        end

        subgraph CommonModule["common module"]
            Auth["common.kubernetes_cluster.auth<br/>K8s Authentication"]
            Kueue["common.kueue<br/>LocalQueue Integration"]
            GenCert["common.utils.generate_cert<br/>TLS Certificate Generation"]
            Widgets["common.widgets<br/>Jupyter ipywidgets UI"]
        end

        Cluster -->|authenticates via| Auth
        Cluster -->|queue assignment| Kueue
        Cluster -->|TLS setup| GenCert
        Cluster -->|notebook UI| Widgets
    end

    %% External CRDs consumed
    User[Data Scientist / User] -->|Python API| Cluster
    GenYAML -->|generates| RayClusterCR["RayCluster CR<br/>ray.io/v1"]
    AppWrapper -->|generates| AppWrapperCR["AppWrapper CR<br/>workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta2"]
    Kueue -->|reads| LocalQueueCR["LocalQueue CR<br/>kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1"]

    %% K8s API interactions
    Auth -->|connects to| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS"]
    RayClusterCR -->|submitted to| K8sAPI
    AppWrapperCR -->|submitted to| K8sAPI

    %% Operator reconciliation
    K8sAPI -->|reconciles| KubeRayOp["KubeRay Operator"]
    K8sAPI -->|reconciles| CFOperator["CodeFlare Operator"]
    KubeRayOp -->|creates| RayHead["Ray Head Pod"]
    KubeRayOp -->|creates| RayWorkers["Ray Worker Pods"]
    KubeRayOp -->|creates| HeadSvc["{cluster}-head-svc<br/>6379, 8265, 10001"]

    %% Dashboard access
    RayClient -->|submits jobs| RayDashboard["Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP"]
    Cluster -->|status check| RayDashboard
    RayDashboard -.->|via| Route["OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS"]

